cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.DC, cs.NE, cs.AR 

This paper is about deep learning and its optimization, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper specifically focuses on Convolutional Neural Networks (cs.CV), Recurrent Neural Networks (cs.NE), and Multilayer Perceptron (cs.NE) training and inference primitives. The paper also mentions the use of a tensor compiler (cs.DC) to further optimize performance. Finally, the paper provides proof-of-concept CNN kernels targeting GPUs (cs.AR).
